    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, wash, then trim the base from your <strong>pak choi</strong>, then separate the individual leaves and discard the base[s]</p><p>Trim your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong>, then cut each<strong> </strong>spring onion into thirds</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
