            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>pork loin steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rub the <strong>pork loin steak[s]</strong> with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season both sides with <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the steak[s] and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until browned and cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1629.-step-3-x200.jpg",
