        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once sticky, remove the pan from the heat and add the<strong> rested pork steak[s]</strong></p><p>Turn the <strong>pork steak[s]</strong> in the sticky sauce until fully coated – these are your <strong>sticky Chinese-style pork steak[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>sticky Chinese-style pork steak[s] </strong>finely into strips on a clean board</p><p>Add your <strong>black sesame seeds </strong>to the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> and fluff with a fork – this is your <strong>sesame rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
