    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> sliced sticky Chinese-style pork steak[s]</strong> over the<strong> sesame rice </strong>and drizzle with any <strong>remaining sticky sauce</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> sesame pak choi & spring onions</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
